author: Play On Tabletop
description:
This series brought to you by Frontline Gaming. Game mat and terrain are both sold on their web store: https://store.frontlinegaming.org/?ref=oqafoc17 Check out their terrain and there upcoming events!
===============GAME INFO=============

Game one of our brand new 40k Studio League.  Over the next three months four players will compete through 9 games to crown one champion!   Tune in each friday for the next game in the series.
Tak - Space Marines
Nick- T'au
Tycho - Tyranids
Mubin - Custodes.
